          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1711468247819-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cover your <strong>blanched peas</strong> with <strong>boiled water</strong> and set aside until later</p><p>Grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1711468276060-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
