      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain the <strong>peas</strong>, then add them to the pan with the <strong>grated carrot</strong>,<strong> chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>ginger</strong> and cook for 5-6 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
